								"name": "Paragraph",
								"type": "textarea",
								"html": "<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\tEchelon seeks to mobilize the next generation for The Salvation Army of Greater Charlotte by providing opportunities for young professionals to engage with the organization through fellowship and networking, donations and fundraising, and service and volunteering. These activities directly support Salvation Army services in the Charlotte community. Whether we are serving, attending one of our social events, or raising money, you will find Echelon is a connected community full of people who are making a difference.\n</p>",
